      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity, Poiseuille flow) demonstrating correct implementation of governing equations at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark verification cases were executed prior to the hemolysis simulations. Results matched analytical solutions within expected numerical precision, confirming code correctness."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
