      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for hemolysis index and shear stress QoIs; GCI < 5% on fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (3.2M, 7.8M, 18.4M cells). GCI for hemolysis index was 3.1% between medium and fine meshes; fine mesh selected for production runs."
    },
    {
