      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid properties) are documented and replicated in the simulation within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions (2.5 L/min, 3500 RPM, bovine blood analog) were reproduced in the CFD model. Inlet velocity profiles derived from PIV measurements."
