      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Hemolysis index and volume-averaged shear stress are directly linked to the clinical endpoint of red blood cell damage in CPB devices.",
      "rationale": "The selected QoIs (NIH, scalar shear stress) are standard metrics for CPB hemolysis assessment per ASTM F1841 and align with FDA guidance on computational modeling of blood-contacting devices."
