    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility for its intended use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team notes that this model has been applied in clinical research to support device design decisions, and the evidence package supports continued use within the documented operating envelope.",
